acquisition system treats 92 PMT signals from 61 PDCs + 30 SASs + 1
neutron detector, and it is developed based on SpaceWire spacecraft
communication network. Most of the signal processing is done by digital
circuits in Field Programmable Gate Arrays (FPGAs). This enables the
reduction of the mass, the space and the power consumption. The
